snippet.textDisplay: This is a great video and teach valuable information about how the coronavirus SARS-COV-2 leads to the terrible disease named COVID-19 and the key structures proteins as  spikes (S) [where the name Corona in latin comes from], membrane (M) and the envelope (E).
